    {"entityTypeName":"CaseEvidenceArtifact","description":"Immutable accepted case evidence version and provenance metadata.","attributes":[{"name":"artifactId","dataType":"string","required":true},{"name":"caseId","dataType":"string","required":true},{"name":"versionId","dataType":"string","required":true},{"name":"sha256","dataType":"string","required":true},{"name":"classification","dataType":"string","required":true},{"name":"storageLocation","dataType":"string","required":true}]},
